FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Me can't shoot from back here and ting, Niko.
~z~Boy, me tink me was gone den, ya know?
~z~I cannot talk about this now. Goodbye, Jacob.
~z~Ya keep shooting and this transport aint gonna be in no good shape at all.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你保持射击，这车会被打得体无完肤。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Jacob, you and Roman stay back. I'm going in to get Pegorino.
~z~I'm getting sick of killing these lackeys, where is Pegorino?
~z~We need fe be nearer to de pussyhole ya know. Me need more speed!
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我们要跟紧那个贱人。来点速度！

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Damn, I was meant to protect her...
~z~What? We want get dis raas clot too ya know, Niko.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~什么？我们也想干掉这个混蛋，Niko。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Wait for me, I'm on my way. What is Roman doing there? This is not the place for him.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~等我，我这就来。Roman过去干啥？那不是他该去的地方。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Jacob, the best way to help me is to keep my cousin alive. I don't want to lose him as well.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~Jacob，保证我哥活着就是对我最大的帮助。我不想再失去他了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Alright, cousin. We hear anything. We will come to help you.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~好吧，老弟。有什么不对，我们马上来救你。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Let I show these ras clots how fe shoot a piece.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~让这些渣渣瞧瞧枪是怎么打的。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~You're nothing but a two bit hood.
~z~Jacob get de boat and ting. He ain't going far, rasta.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我看到他的船了，他走不远的，兄弟。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Come on, NB. You can do it.
~z~Boy, dat was close and ting rasta.
~z~He be inna some building in Koresh Square. We keep an eye out pon it.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~他在Koresh广场的一栋楼里。我们正盯着呢。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Get me close to dis bumba clot.
~z~Also, figure out an exit strategy. When this guy is dead, I'm not going to want to hang around long.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~还有，找个撤退方案。等他死了，我可不想在这里久留。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Cha, Niko. Watch out for de missile.
~z~I an' I get him, rasta. He going fe crash pon the island.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我看见他了，兄弟。他要在岛上抛锚了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Jacob nah mek no boy shoot after him.
~z~Niko, I and Roman have found one a dat ras clot Pegorino's men, seen?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~Niko，我和Roman找到了那个混蛋Pegorino的手下，懂？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Rhaatid, dere be a missile heading at us.
~z~Come on, Niko. Wine up on him.
~z~Jacob's gone. How many people have to die today?
~z~There ain't no way we going be finding these boys if ya lose de transport ya know, rasta.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~跟丢他们的车，我们就别想找到他们了，兄弟。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Let Jacob stop these bumba clots from shooting after us.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~让我杀了这些在后面射我们的人。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Stay here, I need to end this by myself.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~待在这里，我要亲手结束这一切。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~None of you are going to stop me from killing Jimmy P.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你们谁也别想阻止我杀Jimmy P。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Look out for de rocket now, man.
~z~Boy, dis no good for me heart.
~z~Yeah man, me get de ras clot. See him a crash pon de island?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~耶，兄弟，我找到那个混蛋了。等着他靠岸弃船吧。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Why didn't you just hit me instead?
~z~Pegorino is mine, no one can keep me from him.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~Pegorino是我的猎物，没人可以阻止我。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Cha, get closer to de ras so him can feel me teeth.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~嘿，离那个贱人近点，让他尝尝我的厉害。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Give me some heat, Niko. We need fe catch up pon him.
~z~Ya nah shoot at us no more!
~z~Yo man, I try keep dis ras clot off of us, ya know.
~z~Faster, rasta, faster. Catch up pon him.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~再快点，兄弟，再快点。追上他们。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I'm either dying here or killing Jimmy P. I ain't backing down.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~今天要么我死，要么Jimmy P死。我不会放弃的。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~If dat hits us, we're fucked and ting, Niko.
~z~I'll swim if I have to. Urgh.
~z~Get I in range, ya know breda.
~z~Jacob stopping these ras clots from taking us down and ting.
~z~I need fe get closer to get dis ras clot.
~z~Alright, me breda. Dat blood clot be inna de place. I an' I been following him for a time, seen?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~好了，好兄弟。那个狗逼就在这里。我们跟踪他有段时间了，懂？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I'll give fifty Gs to the man that drops this fuck.
~z~Lord protect us. We shot and ting.
~z~Dis how we dweet inna Jam Down!
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~这就是牙买加人的解决方式！

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~He backing you up, rasta. I an' I both be, seen? One love.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~他是来支援的，兄弟。我们都是你的后盾，懂吧。再见。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~A rocket be heading at us, rasta.
~z~Get I closer for de shot, cousin.
~z~Me tink his next step is wit Pegorino. We follow him there, seen?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我想他们待会儿会去找Pegorino。我们跟着他去，懂？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I and I be de righteous dread!
~z~Thank you, both of you. But I do not think this is the place for you, Roman. This is too dangerous.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~谢谢，谢谢你们。但你不该一起来的，Roman。太危险了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Land pon de Island mek we finish him.
~z~You are my cousin Niko, and Kate died at my wedding. I'm helping you.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你是我的堂弟，Niko。而Kate死在了我的婚礼上。我要帮你。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Niko, we see the boat! Me and Jacob are going after it!
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~Niko，我们看见船了！我和Jacob会跟着的！

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~We were so close, I thought we had him.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我们就差一点，就差一点就追上了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Will someone get rid of this dickhead already?
~z~Ya see, after dat heroin deal, Dimitri's hangin out wit Pegorino now.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你看，在那次海洛因交易后，Dimitri就和Pegorino在一块了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~You motherfucker. Don't think for a second that this was anyone's fault but your own.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你个杂种。事到如今怪不了别人，全怪你。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I know. Jacob was a good friend to both of us. Call me soon, Niko.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我知道。Jacob是咱俩的好朋友。待会联系，Niko。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Rhaatid, we losing him. Get closer now rasta.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~妈的，要跟丢了。离他再近点，兄弟。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Rhaatid, see him dere. Ya have fe stick to him me breda.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我去，他来了。一定要跟住他，好兄弟。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Niko, you need fe get closer. We can't be losing him.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~Niko，你得再近点。我们不能跟丢他。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Dis a black day me breda, a black day.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~真是黑暗的一天，兄弟，黑暗透了。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Ya need fe give I and I some cover else we never be able fe follow em.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你得掩护我，不然我们不可能跟上他。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I'd clip that bitch again if I had the chance.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~如果有第二次，我还是会杀了那个婊子。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~There must be a safe way to catch this guy.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~一定有一条安全的路去抓住那个人。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~It's not worth it. None of this is worth it.
~z~I tink dis boy gonna lead me to right where Jimmy and Dimitri are.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我想这个小子会带我们去Jimmy和Dimitri在的地方。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Well, we did not have him. He is still alive. I'll see you both later.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~好吧，我们没抓住他。他还活着。我们之后见。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Shit, I wish I'd have hit you at the wedding.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~操，真后悔没在婚礼上杀了你。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Get in closer, Niko. We losing the ras clot.
~z~I an' I will find dat ras clot again.
~z~No thanks to you, you trying to ditch me?
~z~Couldn't you have killed me, you dumb shit?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你怎么没把我杀了呢，傻逼玩意？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Boy, me don't like dis at all.
~z~Air unit seven-b has been engaged. This is a potential terrorist situation.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~空中单位7-b已经启用了。这是潜在的恐怖主义局势。;//未使用

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Yeah, me tink so too, ya know me breda.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~是，我也这么想，你知道的，兄弟。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I wanted out and you killed someone I cared about. It's over for you now, Jimmy.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我想要退出，但你杀了我在乎的人。现在你死定了，Jimmy。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~There'll be another chance to find him cousin.
~z~Alright, dis is where he be going. What's the plan, Niko?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~好了，这就是他的目的地了。什么打算，Niko？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Are you trying to kill us too?
~z~Come on, Niko. Me can't get no shot from here.
~z~How you gonna get by in this country if you ain't gonna go after the big money?
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~要是不想赚大钱，怎么在这个国家生存？

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Me knew you'd find a way, me bredren. Take control of dis ting. You better at driving than me.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~就知道你能杀出来，好兄弟。飞机你开吧，你技术比我好。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~You're checking your blind spots, right Niko?
~z~Air unit seven-b has taken damage. Brace position! Brace position!
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~空中单位7-b受损。Brace！Brace！;//Brace position是面临坠机需要做的保护性动作

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I an' I need fe kill dis teeth affa de transport.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~在运输后我想我需要杀了这些混蛋。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~You coulda worked with me and everything woulda been gravy.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~你跟我合作的话大家都能吃肉。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Would the black Huntley please pull over to the central reservation. You have been flagged for reckless driving.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~请布莱克亨特利饭店把车停在中央预订处好吗?你因鲁莽驾驶而被警告。;//未使用

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Shoot that fuck before he kills us all.
~z~Put de chopper pon di island, mek we end dis now.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~把直升机降落在岛上，我们现在去结束这一切。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Fuck, we got a tail. Better lose this piece of shit on the way back to the Peg. I don't wanna be late.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~操，有人跟踪。最好在回去找Peg的路上甩掉他们。我可不想迟到。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~I just got married. I can't die here.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我才刚刚结婚。我不能死在这里。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Please don't kill us, please don't kill us, please don't kill us.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~求求别杀了我们，求求别杀了我们，求求别杀了我们。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Your problem is you like killing too much.
~z~Step on the accelerator, Niko. Get closer to de fool.
~z~Yo, two can play at this game ya know, star.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~哟，两个可以玩这个游戏。;//未使用

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Niko, de boat get away and ting. We ain't gonna get him, yo.
~z~Cousin, me and Jacob are here to help you.
~z~Poor girl, she should never have got close to me...
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~可怜的女孩，她本可以不走进我的生活的...

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Cha, Niko. Don't be losing de bumba clot boy.
~z~I ain't got nothing left. You better kill me.
FIN1CAU.translated: ~z~我现在一无所有。你杀了我啊。

FIN1CAU.original: ~z~Come on me breda. Get inna the car.
~z~Don't think I don't know how to fight.
